═══════════════════════════════════════════════
DATABASE MIGRATIONS
═══════════════════════════════════════════════

Extend the default Laravel users table with:
  username              string unique
  display_name          string nullable
  pronouns              string nullable
  bio                   string(160) nullable
  country               string nullable
  city                  string nullable
  location_hidden       boolean default false
  avatar_path           string nullable
  profile_visibility    enum: public/members/connections default members
  messaging_permission  enum: everyone/connections/no_one default connections
  show_online           boolean default false
  intents               json nullable
  ghost_mode            boolean default false
  onboarding_completed  boolean default false
  is_suspended          boolean default false

Create these additional tables:

connections
  id, requester_id (FK users), receiver_id (FK users)
  status: enum pending/accepted/declined/blocked
  timestamps

conversations
  id, timestamps

conversation_participants (pivot)
  conversation_id, user_id, joined_at

messages
  id, conversation_id (FK), sender_id (FK users)
  body text (encrypted via Laravel cast)
  read_at nullable timestamp
  auto_delete_at nullable timestamp
  timestamps

spaces
  id, name, slug unique, description text nullable
  type: enum public/private default public
  creator_id (FK users)
  avatar_path nullable
  timestamps

space_members (pivot)
  space_id, user_id
  role: enum member/moderator default member
  joined_at

space_posts
  id, space_id (FK), user_id (FK)
  body text
  timestamps

reports
  id, reporter_id (FK users), reported_user_id (FK users)
  reason string, description text nullable
  status: enum pending/reviewed/resolved default pending
  timestamps

trusted_contacts
  id, user_id (FK)
  name string, phone string
  timestamps

safety_checkins
  id, user_id (FK), trusted_contact_id (FK)
  check_in_at timestamp
  status: enum active/safe/alerted default active
  timestamps

═══════════════════════════════════════════════
ROUTES & PAGES
═══════════════════════════════════════════════

PUBLIC (guest middleware):
  GET /              → Pages/Landing.tsx
  GET /join          → Pages/Auth/Register.tsx
  GET /login         → Pages/Auth/Login.tsx

AUTHENTICATED (auth middleware):
  GET /onboarding    → Pages/Onboarding/Index.tsx (4-step, forced)
  GET /home          → Pages/Home.tsx
  GET /members       → Pages/Members/Index.tsx
  GET /members/:username → Pages/Members/Show.tsx
  GET /connections   → Pages/Connections.tsx
  GET /messages      → Pages/Messages/Index.tsx
  GET /messages/:username → Pages/Messages/Show.tsx
  GET /spaces        → Pages/Spaces/Index.tsx
  GET /spaces/create → Pages/Spaces/Create.tsx
  GET /spaces/:slug  → Pages/Spaces/Show.tsx
  GET /profile       → Pages/Profile/Index.tsx
  GET /settings/profile  → Pages/Settings/Profile.tsx
  GET /settings/privacy  → Pages/Settings/Privacy.tsx
  GET /settings/safety   → Pages/Settings/Safety.tsx

ADMIN:
  GET  /admin/login      → Pages/Admin/Login.tsx
  GET  /admin/dashboard  → Pages/Admin/Dashboard.tsx
  GET  /admin/users      → Pages/Admin/Users.tsx
  GET  /admin/reports    → Pages/Admin/Reports.tsx
  GET  /admin/spaces     → Pages/Admin/Spaces.tsx

