═══════════════════════════════════════════════
LANDING PAGE — Awwwards-level design spec
═══════════════════════════════════════════════
This is the most important page. It must feel like entering
a place, not buying a product. Use the following structure:

NAVBAR
  - Logo: "HURU" in Fraunces italic, amber color
  - Links: About · Spaces · Safety
  - Right: "Join" button (amber outlined) + "Login" (ghost)
  - Sticky, dark bg, 1px bottom border rgba(255,255,255,0.06)

HERO SECTION
  - Full viewport height
  - Background: #0C0A09 with a radial amber glow behind the 
    headline (rgba(217,119,6,0.12) circle, 800px, centered)
  - Large editorial headline in Fraunces italic:
    "You deserve
     a safe place
     to just be."
  - Each line animates in with staggered fade+translateY on load
    (CSS only, animation-delay: 0s / 0.15s / 0.3s)
  - Subheadline in Plus Jakarta Sans 300:
    "HURU connects LGBTQ+ people worldwide — 
     privately, safely, without compromise."
  - Two CTAs side by side:
    Primary: "Create your profile" → /join (amber bg)
    Secondary: "See how it works" → smooth scroll to #how
  - Below CTAs: small text in muted color:
    "No real name required. No data sold. Ever."
  - Floating member count badge bottom-right of hero:
    pulsing green dot + "2,400+ members worldwide"
    (hardcoded for now, replace with live count later)

HOW IT WORKS SECTION (#how)
  - 3 columns, icon + heading + short paragraph each
  - Column 1: "Stay anonymous" — username only, no real name needed
  - Column 2: "Find your people" — filter by intent, country, vibe
  - Column 3: "Stay safe" — ghost mode, check-in timer, trusted contacts

SPACES PREVIEW SECTION
  - Section heading: "Join spaces built for you"
  - Horizontal scroll row of 4–5 space cards (hardcoded examples):
    Mental Health · Coming Out · Nairobi Meetups · Trans Support · Book Club
  - Each card: dark surface, space name, member count, join button
  - Faint amber glow on hover

SAFETY PROMISE SECTION
  - Dark teal background (#0D2D2A)
  - Heading: "Safety is not a feature. It's the foundation."
  - 3 trust badges: No real names · Messages encrypted · Ghost mode
  - Short paragraph about the mission

SUPPORT SECTION (Buy Me a Coffee)
  - Heading: "Built by one developer. Powered by community."
  - Paragraph: "HURU is free, ad-free, and built in Nairobi for
    the world. Your support keeps it running and independent."
  - Button: "☕ Buy us a coffee" → https://buymeacoffee.com/huruapp
  - Secondary line: "M-Pesa and card accepted"

FOOTER
  - Logo + tagline
  - Links: Privacy · Safety · Contact · GitHub
  - "Built in Nairobi 🇰🇪 for the world"
  - Small BMaC link in footer too

═══════════════════════════════════════════════
ONBOARDING — 4-step forced flow
═══════════════════════════════════════════════
Redirect to /onboarding after register if onboarding_completed = false.
Block all other auth routes until complete.

Step 1 — Your identity
  Username (validated unique), display name (optional), pronouns

Step 2 — About you
  Bio (160 char limit with counter), country, city (optional),
  hide location toggle

Step 3 — Your intentions
  Multi-select pill buttons (not checkboxes):
  Friendship · Support · Dating · Community · Just browsing

Step 4 — Stay safe
  Brief explanation of ghost mode and check-in timer
  Toggle: enable ghost mode by default?
  "Finish setup" button → sets onboarding_completed = true
  → redirects to /home

Design: dark full-screen, progress dots at top, 
step slides in from right, back/next navigation,
amber CTA buttons.

═══════════════════════════════════════════════
MEMBER DISCOVERY (/members)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════
- Grid of member cards (respect profile_visibility)
- Each card: avatar (or default initial avatar), username,
  pronouns, country, intent pills, Connect button
- Filters sidebar: country, intent, online only
- ghost_mode = true → user does NOT appear in this list
- is_suspended = true → user does NOT appear

═══════════════════════════════════════════════
MESSAGING
═══════════════════════════════════════════════
- Real-time via Laravel Reverb
- Encrypted body (decrypt on read, never store plain)
- Auto-delete: user can set a message expiry 
  (1 hour / 24 hours / 7 days / never)
- A scheduled job (every 5 minutes) deletes 
  messages where auto_delete_at < now()
- Read receipts (read_at timestamp)
- No message editing — delete only

═══════════════════════════════════════════════
SAFETY CENTER (/settings/safety)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════
Ghost mode toggle
  → When on: remove from member discovery, 
    hide online status, profile shows 
    "This profile is private" to non-connections

Trusted contacts
  → Add up to 3 contacts (name + phone)
  → These receive an SMS (via Africa's Talking API 
    or Twilio) if a check-in is missed

Check-in timer
  → User sets a time (e.g. "Check in within 2 hours")
  → A countdown is shown on their dashboard
  → If they don't tap "I'm safe" before it expires,
    trusted contacts are alerted
  → Implement with a Laravel scheduled job

Delete account
  → Soft delete: anonymize all data, 
    set username to [deleted], null all PII fields
  → Hard delete option: fully wipe after 30-day grace period

═══════════════════════════════════════════════
ADMIN PANEL
═══════════════════════════════════════════════
Simple, functional. No need for elaborate design.
Protected by separate admin middleware.

Dashboard: total users, active today, pending reports, spaces count
Users: paginated table, search, suspend/unsuspend toggle
Reports: list by status, view details, mark reviewed/resolved
Spaces: list, delete, feature toggle

Seed one admin: email=admin@huru.app password=Admin1234!
Add warning in README to change before production.

═══════════════════════════════════════════════
PRIVACY & SECURITY RULES
═══════════════════════════════════════════════
- Email is never shown to other users — ever
- Username is the only public identity
- Sanctum tokens stored in memory only (not localStorage)
- All avatar uploads: strip EXIF via intervention/image v3
- Messages encrypted at rest with Laravel encrypt() cast
- ghost_mode users excluded from all discovery endpoints
- Suspended users excluded from all public endpoints
- Admin panel on /admin — note in README to change pre-launch
- Rate limit: POST /api/messages → 60/minute per user

═══════════════════════════════════════════════
BUILD ORDER — follow this exactly
═══════════════════════════════════════════════
Phase 1 (start here):
  1. Wipe old resource-directory migrations, models, controllers,
     seeders, and pages — keep auth scaffold, Inertia config, 
     Tailwind config, folder structure
  2. New migrations in the order listed above
  3. User model with casts (intents → array, body → encrypted)
  4. Fortify + Sanctum auth (register, login, logout, email verify)
  5. Onboarding flow (4 steps, forced redirect)
  6. Profile page + settings pages (profile, privacy)
  7. Landing page (full Awwwards spec above)

Phase 2:
  8. Member discovery + profile view
  9. Connection requests (send, accept, decline, block)
  10. Block list enforcement across all queries

Phase 3:
  11. Reverb WebSocket setup
  12. Conversations + messages (create thread, send, receive live)
  13. Auto-delete job
  14. Read receipts

Phase 4:
  15. Spaces (create, browse, join, post)
  16. Space moderation (moderator role)

Phase 5:
  17. Safety center (ghost mode enforcement, trusted contacts)
  18. Check-in timer + scheduled alert job
  19. Account deletion (soft + hard)

Phase 6:
  20. Admin panel (all sections)
  21. Reports system

